originalText.text: I had a custom motorcycle transported through these people. It arrived damaged. Had a chemical spill on the bottom edge of the saddle bag, the driver claimed was gasoline. But it wasn't on the gas tank at all. Next the driver backed the bike out of a Uhaul truck, and burried the rear fender into the asphalt. Before I booked with these people I asked if they had insurance and they replied YES!!! NOW no one wants to pay for the damages and won't answer emails, and made the phone where it won't accept incoming calls. I would NEVER use these people, unless you just don't care how your stuff arrives.
